        'Non-Commutative Directionality: ij=k, ji=-k reflects the chirality/handedness of rotations on the torus',
        'Four-Component Structure: Real part + three imaginary parts = minimal structure for 3D rotations',
        'The Bindu as Volumetric Void: Center point (0,0) in 2D becomes 3D void when torus embedded in ℝ³',
        'Proto-Rotational Awareness: The implicit capacity to "turn" consciousness back upon itself',
        'Pre-Reflective Self-Reference: "I know that I know" exists before explicit topological recognition',
        'Undifferentiated Circulation: The torus experienced from inside before seeing it as object',
        'Generator Seed: i and j as the proto-generators that will trace meridian and longitude',
        'Connection to Spanda Seed: The (0/1) oscillation now gaining quaternionic depth',
        'Relation to QL Position 0: The implicit ground carrying quaternionic potential',
        'Unit Sphere in Quaternion Space: |q|=1 constraint creates 3-sphere S³, whose Hopf fibration reveals torus structure'
    ],
    n.resonances = [
