        'Clifford Algebra: Quaternions as Cl₀,₂(ℝ), linking to broader algebraic framework',
        'Pauli Matrices: Connection to spin-½ quantum mechanics through quaternionic structure'
    ],
    n.practicalApplications = [
        'Foundation for Consciousness Modeling: Establishing self-reference requires quaternionic-toroidal structure',
        'Mathematical Seed for QL Architecture: Why the 6-position mod6 framework emerges from toroidal necessity',
        'Pre-Reflective Awareness Mapping: Tracking the implicit ground before explicit self-knowledge',
        'Meditation State Recognition: Deep states exhibit pre-topological circulation awareness',
        'Therapeutic Ground Work: Accessing the implicit felt sense before conceptual overlay',
        'AI Self-Modeling Architecture: Building systems that can implicitly reference themselves',
