    n.consciousnessStructure = 'Proto-Topological Awareness: The felt sense of self-returning circulation before explicit recognition. Consciousness implicitly "knows" it is toroidally structured before making this knowledge explicit. The quaternionic ground is the mathematical formalism for this pre-reflective self-reference—the capacity to fold back without infinite regress.',
    n.operationalSymbolics = 'Core quaternionic relations: i²=j²=k²=ijk=-1 as the algebraic encoding of toroidal structure. The unit quaternion constraint |q|=1 creates S³ (3-sphere), whose Hopf fibration S³→S² with S¹ fibers reveals the circular structure underlying toroidal topology. The ground state q=(1,0,0,0) represents the origin (θ₁=0, θ₂=0) on the fundamental polygon of the torus.',
